Package net.sf.mmm.util.lang.base Description

Contains the basic implementation of the Util Lang API.

Util Lang Base

This package contains the implementations of the utilities offered by the Util Lang API.
Further the AbstractCharSequence helps to write implementations of the interface CharSequence easily.
